750
01:00:22,730 --> 01:00:25,900
Yes, I think you're right.
You do need some more time.

751
01:00:25,980 --> 01:00:28,480
- Listen. Don't worry. I'll handle that.
- Good man.

752
01:00:28,570 --> 01:00:31,190
