875
01:10:30,710 --> 01:10:33,630
- Social intercourse.
- There's somebody under the table.

876
01:10:33,710 --> 01:10:36,960
- Which table?
- This table!

877
01:10:44,640 --> 01:10:46,800
Is this the palazzo of Signor Casanova?

878
01:10:46,890 --> 01:10:50,390
